  12:../../libDaisy//src/per/dac.h ****  ** For now only Normal Mode is supported,
  13:../../libDaisy//src/per/dac.h ****  ** Sample and hold mode provides reduced power consumption, but requires a bit more setup.
  14:../../libDaisy//src/per/dac.h ****  **
